      "description": "Pure CSS tabs using radios + :has(). No JS.",
      "markup": "<div class=\"tabs\"><div class=\"tabs-list\" role=\"radiogroup\" aria-label=\"X tabs\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"X\" id=\"X-1\" checked><label for=\"X-1\" class=\"tabs-trigger\">T1</label></div><div class=\"tabs-panel\" data-tab=\"X-1\">\u2026</div></div>",
