        "tabs-trigger",
        "tabs-panel"
      ],
      "attributes": [
        "data-variant=\"underline\"",
        "data-orientation=\"vertical\""
      ],
      "notes": "Selection lives on the native radios. role=tab/tablist/tabpanel are intentionally omitted: CSS cannot keep a static aria-selected in sync with :checked, so the honest, accessible model is a native radiogroup (true ARIA tabs/tabpanels with aria-controls/aria-labelledby require consumer JS to move selection)."
