        "toggle-group-sm",
        "toggle-group-lg"
      ],
      "attributes": [
        "data-variant=\"outline\"",
        "data-orientation=\"vertical\""
      ],
      "notes": "Order is mandatory: each <input> MUST be the immediately-preceding sibling of its <label class=\"toggle-group-item\">. The checked-highlight relies on the adjacent-sibling selector (input:checked + .toggle-group-item), so any element between the input and its label breaks the styling."
